title: 2 Months Free Rent! Mobile Home Spaces in the Mendocino Redwoods
posting_body: ['Mobile home space for rent in the small town of Branscomb just 15 minutes away from the town of Laytonville and 15 miles from the ocean in the heart of Mendocino County.', 'Doubles and singles are available.', 'Beautiful park surrounded by nature.', 'Bring your home or trailer!', 'Branscomb is located in Northern California, only 15 minutes from Highway 101.', 'Branscomb is the ideal central location from which to enjoy the Redwoods and the exceptional beauty of Mendocino County.', 'Within biking distance of the mobile park is the Admiral Standley State Recreation Area home to ancient old growth redwood trees.', 'Driving north from Laytonville on the 101 an hour leads you to The Avenue of the Giants and the Eel River, to the south award-winning wineries, and to the west is the rugged Mendocino Coast.', 'We invite you to stay, play and enjoy from your central location in Branscomb!', 'Water, Electricity and Garbage to be paid by the tenant.', '2 month free on a 12-month rental agreement.', 'Or month to month', 'Currently available:', '+ MH space: $395/month + Utilities', 'All spaces accommodate up to 50ft vehicle and are full hookups', 'All accommodate 30/50amp."']
